- Read all new filter params from `searchParams` and pass to `pageAssets`.
- Wire sort dropdown to URL params (replacing the search-mode-only sort).

### Acceptance criteria

- FilterBar shows Photo / Video / All toggle; selecting "Video" adds `media_type=video` to URL
  and grid shows only videos.
- Camera make dropdown shows only makes present in the library.
- ISO range inputs reflect actual min/max from facets.
- All filters compose: selecting Sony + ISO 800-3200 + Video shows only Sony videos in that
  ISO range.
- Removing a chiclet clears that filter and refetches.
- Sort dropdown works in browse mode and persists in URL.
- Filters panel expand/collapse state persists across page loads.

